  <li>Hence,â€¦ ç”±äº</li>
  <li>[something] yields [something]  â€¦è¡¨æ˜â€¦</li>
  <li>However, [something is true], therefore, [another thing] holds. â€¦æˆç«‹ï¼Œå› æ­¤ï¼Œâ€¦æˆç«‹</li>
  <li>Thus,â€¦ é‚£ä¹ˆ</li>
